Vodacom Business has unveiled its Black Friday 2019 deals, with a range of discounted smartphone contracts on offer. The contracts include data-centric offerings paired with the latest Samsung, Apple, and Huawei smartphones. It is also offering a “3 Million Megs Promo”, which is a data contract that will give users a total of 1 Million Megabytes of data per year. The contract comprises of an 85GB subscription bundle per month for 36 months. “The 3 Million Megs Promo deals are only available to registered business customers. Existing Vodacom Business customers who are due for an upgrade can purchase the 3 Million Megs Promo deals.” A selection of the Black Friday specials from Vodacom Business are listed below. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-330685" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/67567-Black-Friday-640X430.jpg" alt="Vodacom" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/67567-Black-Friday-640X430.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/67567-Black-Friday-640X430-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/67567-Black-Friday-640X430-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-330597 size-large" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Vodacom-2-640x384.jpg" alt="Vodacom" width="640" height="384" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Vodacom-2-640x384.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Vodacom-2-600x360.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Vodacom-2-768x461.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Vodacom-2-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Vodacom-2-2048x1229.jpg 2048w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/upload